text: The Wiesbaden Tennis Open is a tournament for professional female tennis players played on outdoor clay courts. The event is classified as a $60,000 ITF Women's Circuit tournament and has been held in Wiesbaden, Germany, since 2012. == Past finals == === Singles === {|class="wikitable" style="font- size:90%" |-
